{"tid":1243939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"參考返聖雄甘地，如果要採用非勇武不合作運動，香港人重有好多野未做？","createTime":"2019-06-19T16:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:31:23.000Z","uid":92479,"like":91,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"374ce1b1153c760a6d54397862a3e5c43cd5d805","tid":1243939,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2b/Ingres_coronation_charles_vii.jpg/250px-Ingres_coronation_charles_vii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F2%2F2b%2FIngres_coronation_charles_vii.jpg%2F250px-Ingres_coronation_charles_vii.jpg&h=a965ce8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不合作運動（英語：Non-cooperation movement），又稱非暴力不合作運動，是世界歷史上第一個全國性的非暴力反抗運動，由律師出身的印度國民大會黨領袖聖雄甘地。他發動和領導了1920&mdash;1922年和1930&mdash;1934年全國範圍的非暴力不合作運動。<br />\n<br />\n第一次世界大戰結束後（1918年），英國對印度的統治轉趨嚴厲，反英運動隨之興起，要求獨立自治的呼聲高張。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>甘地呼籲以非暴力的不合作手段，抵制英國的統治。他要求印度人不納稅、不入公立學校、不到法庭、不入公職、不購買英貨，並多次絕食。<br />\n<br />\n爲了展示抵制英貨的決心，他甚至號召群眾焚燒英國工廠所傾銷給印度人民的衣物及公開製鹽。甘地和平消極抵抗的方法，使當地的殖民政府近乎癱瘓，並讓其飽受各界尤其是英國國內的壓力，迫使英國政府不得不頒布新憲法，讓印度逐漸發展自治體制。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人除左絕食，好似全部野都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3add17f5f8f1dc80a20abfc09828953d61eba57b","tid":1243939,"uid":15646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:19:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9e344566df42dc2fe0ea97ad9b1206b6846a77f","tid":1243939,"uid":92479,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.roadbroads.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/The-Comfort-Zone.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.roadbroads.com%2Fwp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FThe-Comfort-Zone.jpeg&h=3c244fbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd91dd9af29a738fb221a5ee9a7bc21a11b4ef66","tid":1243939,"uid":2607,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:21:06.000Z","msg":"人地對英國佬<br />\n我地對共產黨"},{"pid":"1aaba7b48bb06c794e7d787888a20990b4eeb231","tid":1243939,"uid":140738,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:22:20.000Z","msg":"叫人唔交稅已經講左好耐啦"},{"pid":"01034052b5bfd566e2f55a4750741e7f6735d07b","tid":1243939,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:23:16.000Z","msg":"幾日前已經問緊 但又好似諗唔到啲咩可以做"},{"pid":"f875843890f1b45de2f6397ff5152cf706aa0dee","tid":1243939,"uid":235895,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:24:42.000Z","msg":"不入公職<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把人爭住做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596c121d0c11822cbcd2a304d20a1877f65fd6c3","tid":1243939,"uid":92479,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bd91dd9af29a738fb221a5ee9a7bc21a11b4ef66","tid":1243939,"uid":2607,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:21:06.000Z","msg":"人地對英國佬<br />\n我地對共產黨"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:32:35.000Z","msg":"你講英國會讓步係因為怕人唱，要面？佢地知風險？<br />\n<br />\n但係影響經濟唔關係英定中事<br />\n<br />\n香港係中國提款機，如果經濟有問題會無影響？<br />\n<br />\n香港本身嘅角色就係投資交易轉口，你連經濟都唔影響何來籌碼？經濟如果影響大到搞到美國同中國，就會係籌碼，就好似如果股票交易唔到會有咩問題，要堅持和理非勇武就係學甘地做呢啲野啦，吉唔到肉真係唔知痛<br />\n<br />\n如果唔做呢啲野，重可以點？當你文宣成功6成民眾覺醒，政府真係要理你？真係好大嘅疑問"},{"pid":"d0729d917958ef5089c5c88ba6e5a5bcec2526f1","tid":1243939,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aaba7b48bb06c794e7d787888a20990b4eeb231","tid":1243939,"uid":140738,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:22:20.000Z","msg":"叫人唔交稅已經講左好耐啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"係好耐，不過無咩人敢，成效不足，最終目的係有癱瘓性嘅影響先有用，有做當然好過無嘅，<br />\n<br />\n香港賣地賺錢佔嘅比重高，如果只係少數人唔交，其實無咩作為"},{"pid":"e8acdda613ecb7c19c4a7608c05e759468575827","tid":1243939,"uid":92479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid